<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.4.8">
<l>tūmpuṭaikkai vēḻam veruva maruppocitta</l>
<l>pāmpi ṉaṇaiyā ṉaruḷtanta vānamakku</l>
<l>pūñcerunti poṉcoriyum pullāṇi kaitoḻutēṉ</l>
<l>tēmpa liḷampiṟaiyu meṉṟaṉakkōr ventaḻalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Ah,] the way  that the one on the serpent bed, who broke off a tusk</l>
<l>So that elephant with a hollowed hand[-like trunk] was terrified,</l>
<l>Grant us grace! For me, who worships, hands [joined], in Pullāṇi,</l>
<l>Where flowering pear trees scatter gold,</l>
<l rend="indent">even the waning, thin crescent is a hot flame.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
